  "description": "Hurdy-gurdy buzz bridge showcase — the chien threshold is set at 0.55 so the bridge sits on the edge of activation. Play lightly for a clean medieval drone. Then apply aftertouch or mod wheel to push pressure above the threshold: the trompette erupts from silence. This is the coups de poignet translated to synthesis — a spectral event, not a timbre. CHARACTER macro sweeps buzz intensity; MOVEMENT macro brings the wheel speed alive. The buzz bridge is not decoration. It is the instrument.",
